casebody.data:
ALLY FINANCIAL, INC., Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Bennie G. ELLIS, Jr., Blue Water Partnership Group, LLC, VInny Gebello, Platinum Image Motorsports, LLC, and Skip Vincente, Defendants,
and
Detroit Seafood Market, LLC, Garnishee-Defendant-Appellant. SC: 156816
COA: 332408 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 3, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the October 17, 2017 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
